---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="prose max-w-none text-sm text-gray-300">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>This Privacy Policy explains how WSM Live collects, uses, and discloses your information.</p>
    <h2>Data Collection</h2>
    <p>We may collect usage analytics and external data necessary to display market information. We do not store or share personal data except as required for comments (third-party providers) or service integrations.</p>
    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use third-party services for comments and market data (Disqus, Finnhub, TradingView). Please review their privacy policies before using their services.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Contact: wsmxlive@gmail.com</p>
  </section>
</Layout>